                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 11513/2.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Minister <persName type="from">Bryan</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Legation</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Lisbon</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1908-02-04">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 4, 1908</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Bryan reports having expressed to the Queen Dowager the sympathy of the
                    President and says the funeral obsequies will occur next Saturday. States that
                    the Prince of Wales and other special ambassadors will attend.)</p>
            </div>
        </body>
